    • org.reactfx.EventStreamBase<S>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - type of the first part of events emitted by this event stream.
    B - type of the second part of events emitted by this event stream.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    BiEventStream<A,B>, EventStream<Tuple2<A,B>>

    public abstract class LazilyBoundBiStream<A,B>
extends LazilyBoundStreamBase<java.util.function.BiConsumer<? super A,? super B>>
implements BiEventStream<A,B>
    Bi-event stream that has one or more sources (most commonly event streams, but not necessarily) to which it is subscribed only when it itself has at least one subscriber.
